{"tid":2411874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(溫故知新)新加坡政府毀諾！坦承隨時可查閱人民接觸史 網友氣炸","createTime":"2021-02-17T15:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T00:38:15.000Z","uid":222925,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebad4824fe2fc2682a252134947061f75c15fdf","tid":2411874,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府曾多次向人民保證，政府推出的追蹤新冠肺炎患者接觸史APP「TraceTogether」蒐集到的資料，只會用於追蹤新冠患者接觸史，不會用在其他方面，鼓勵民眾下載，不過，內政部次長陳國明4日在國會接受質詢時承認，警方「調查刑事案件」時也可以取用這些資料，等於推翻先前的保證，引起網友譁然，許多人認為被騙，發文說已怒刪這款APP。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡近八成民眾自願下載TraceTogether，這個APP會記錄使用者去過哪些地方。近日政府宣布，未來必須下載TraceTogether，才能進入各類公共場所，包括超市、工作地點等，因此下載的民眾愈來愈多。<br />\n<br />\nTraceTogether用手機APP或藍牙裝置監控用戶所在地和接觸者。如果用戶確診新冠肺炎，TraceTogether的資料能讓政府很快找到患者接觸過的人，控制疫情傳播。<br />\n<br />\n4日當天，TraceTogether更新了隱私條款，內文寫到：「我們要誠實告訴您，TraceTogether的資料可能用在公民安全受威脅時，新加坡警方依據刑事訴訟法，有權為了刑事調查獲取任何資料，包括TraceTogether的資料。 」<br />\n<br />\n不願具名的新加坡人說：「大多數人不是因為一天到晚被監視而生氣，畢竟到處都有監視器，他們是因為感覺受騙而發火。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5149645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5149645&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a70dec22\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5149645</a>"},{"pid":"0ed9526d6ae8ef8605b4c026d90f5ebce8a61201","tid":2411874,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"d0dce5b6779108826cedf9631e2376526eac825b","tid":2411874,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f1fdae6418c4789e17106eecae697e23145cd9","tid":2411874,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"今日坡仔<br />\n<br />\n洗厠所用品 請用高樂氏、滴露 唔好用潔厠得（威猛先生）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2411750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2411750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"219a3e74d698713820f5d8302fe1c8c8a96806b9","tid":2411874,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0ed9526d6ae8ef8605b4c026d90f5ebce8a61201","tid":2411874,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"WFC"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a0ed7e69bff99a71f230dbfbab49480cb40bb2","tid":2411874,"uid":30988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"極權手法，香港一直加緊學習！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1df3fa4fbeef6af65704dd6d40f1b6ff786d795","tid":2411874,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3a0ed7e69bff99a71f230dbfbab49480cb40bb2","tid":2411874,"uid":30988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"極權手法，香港一直加緊學習！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"新加坡人同香港人好似"},{"pid":"68287331ccf07eb5efc2c7fcd2c5d358107404ee","tid":2411874,"uid":179729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"嬲乜鳩姐，你第一日識自己個政府咩？"},{"pid":"b315be25c099f1532947e0de2f1b864a0bb88311","tid":2411874,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"氣炸又如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9330e5b44ce0091f57c02c4ca60429ad68394df","tid":2411874,"uid":297045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"//新加坡近<span class=\"red\">八成</span>民眾<strong><span class=\"red\">自願</span></strong>下載TraceTogether//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"